[
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=1"
  },
  {
    "text": "Hello. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=9"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm Cindy Clarissa. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=10"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm a software engineer with Core Location. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=11"
  },
  {
    "text": "Today, I'll be talking about ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=14"
  },
  {
    "text": "some cool new things for Core Location this year. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=15"
  },
  {
    "text": "We are introducing two new features ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=18"
  },
  {
    "text": "that may let you power location-based functionality ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=20"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your apps without confronting people ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=23"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the need to grant them as much authorization.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=25"
  },
  {
    "text": "Starting with the first feature, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=29"
  },
  {
    "text": "we are bringing Region-based user notifications to watchOS 8. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=31"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now your Apple Watch app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=35"
  },
  {
    "text": "can remind people to start a workout ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=37"
  },
  {
    "text": "when they arrive at the gym ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=39"
  },
  {
    "text": "or feed the dog when they get home. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=41"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=43"
  },
  {
    "text": "here we have App in the Air using this new feature ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=44"
  },
  {
    "text": "to notify people about their flights ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=47"
  },
  {
    "text": "when they arrive at the airport. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=49"
  },
  {
    "text": "With Region-based user notifications, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=51"
  },
  {
    "text": "the system can present spatially relevant information ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=53"
  },
  {
    "text": "on behalf of your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=56"
  },
  {
    "text": "without it having \"always\" authorization. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=58"
  },
  {
    "text": "To learn more ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=61"
  },
  {
    "text": "about how you can adopt Region-based user notifications ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=62"
  },
  {
    "text": "for watchOS, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=64"
  },
  {
    "text": "check out the session \"What's New in watchOS.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=66"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now let's talk about the main topic of this session. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=69"
  },
  {
    "text": "We're introducing a new way to request location ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=72"
  },
  {
    "text": "that gives people more control over their data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=75"
  },
  {
    "text": "but, at the same time, gives more functionalities to your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=78"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll begin by talking ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=82"
  },
  {
    "text": "about today's state of location authorization ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=83"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the motivation behind our new feature. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=85"
  },
  {
    "text": "In iOS 14, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=88"
  },
  {
    "text": "when an app requests for location authorization, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=90"
  },
  {
    "text": "an initial prompt shows up ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=92"
  },
  {
    "text": "and people have the ability to choose from Allow Once, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=94"
  },
  {
    "text": "While in Use, or Don't Allow authorization. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=98"
  },
  {
    "text": "And with last year's new feature, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=102"
  },
  {
    "text": "people have the ability to control their precision ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=104"
  },
  {
    "text": "of the location being sent to your app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=107"
  },
  {
    "text": "Some of you may have noticed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=109"
  },
  {
    "text": "that people select Allow Once on your app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=111"
  },
  {
    "text": "and it could be ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=114"
  },
  {
    "text": "that they don't think giving when-in-use authorization ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=115"
  },
  {
    "text": "is necessary to your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=117"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=119"
  },
  {
    "text": "a pet store app might request location authorization ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=120"
  },
  {
    "text": "to determine the closest pet store near them, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=123"
  },
  {
    "text": "but it doesn't require their location ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=126"
  },
  {
    "text": "when they are just browsing for different cat food options. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=128"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this case, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=130"
  },
  {
    "text": "people using this app might be more likely to select Allow Once ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=131"
  },
  {
    "text": "or Don't Allow authorization. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=136"
  },
  {
    "text": "If people select Allow Once, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=139"
  },
  {
    "text": "we would grant location authorization ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=141"
  },
  {
    "text": "for the duration that they are using your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=143"
  },
  {
    "text": "But your app will lose authorization ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=146"
  },
  {
    "text": "when it enters the background. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=148"
  },
  {
    "text": "This could lead to multiple location authorization requests, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=150"
  },
  {
    "text": "which may negatively impact the user experience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=154"
  },
  {
    "text": "In another case, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=157"
  },
  {
    "text": "you might notice that someone who is tired of the prompts ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=158"
  },
  {
    "text": "might select Don't Allow ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=161"
  },
  {
    "text": "to prevent the prompts from being shown again. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=163"
  },
  {
    "text": "This could result in having to send people ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=165"
  },
  {
    "text": "to Settings to authorize for locations later. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=168"
  },
  {
    "text": "As privacy continues to be an important priority for Apple, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=171"
  },
  {
    "text": "we thought, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=175"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"How can we give more controls ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=176"
  },
  {
    "text": "without hindering user-experience?” ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=178"
  },
  {
    "text": "Can we provide an easy and friendly way ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=180"
  },
  {
    "text": "to authorize location ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=183"
  },
  {
    "text": "only at the moment when its needed? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=184"
  },
  {
    "text": "Starting in iOS 15, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=187"
  },
  {
    "text": "we're introducing CLLocationButton for UIKit ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=189"
  },
  {
    "text": "and LocationButton for SwiftUI ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=192"
  },
  {
    "text": "to tackle the pain points I've mentioned. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=194"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here, we have a Park Finder app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=196"
  },
  {
    "text": "that finds the closest park nearby. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=198"
  },
  {
    "text": "At the bottom, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=201"
  },
  {
    "text": "we have a blue Location Button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=202"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the title \"Current Location\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=203"
  },
  {
    "text": "next to the arrow glyph. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=206"
  },
  {
    "text": "When I press on the button, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=207"
  },
  {
    "text": "Park Finder is able to get my current location ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=209"
  },
  {
    "text": "and show a map view of all the parks nearby. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=212"
  },
  {
    "text": "A location arrow at the top left ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=215"
  },
  {
    "text": "will turn blue to call to the user's attention ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=217"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the authorization they just have granted.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=220"
  },
  {
    "text": "One thing to note ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=223"
  },
  {
    "text": "is that Location Button is actually giving your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=224"
  },
  {
    "text": "Allow-Once authorization ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=227"
  },
  {
    "text": "without making people go through the prompt each time. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=229"
  },
  {
    "text": "Later, I will go over about how this would affect ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=232"
  },
  {
    "text": "your existing authorization status. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=235"
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll be bringing Location Button to watchOS, iOS, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=238"
  },
  {
    "text": "macOS with Catalyst, and iPad apps on Mac. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=241"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, let's dive into the API ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=245"
  },
  {
    "text": "and how you can add CLLocationButton to your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=247"
  },
  {
    "text": "CLLocationButton is part of the CoreLocationUI framework. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=249"
  },
  {
    "text": "Similar to the UIButton, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=253"
  },
  {
    "text": "CLLocationButton is derived from UIControls. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=255"
  },
  {
    "text": "So, you're able to use UIControl functionalities with the button. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=258"
  },
  {
    "text": "In addition, we have four properties ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=262"
  },
  {
    "text": "that are specific to our button. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=264"
  },
  {
    "text": "We have CLLocationButtonIcon to set the type of the arrow, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=266"
  },
  {
    "text": "CLLocationLabel to set the label of the button, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=271"
  },
  {
    "text": "a cornerRadius to set the roundness of the button, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=276"
  },
  {
    "text": "and lastly, we have fontSize to set the size of the label.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=280"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now that I went through a brief overview, you might wonder, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=284"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"How can I receive location with CLLocationButton?\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=288"
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, it's similar to requesting location with a UIButton. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=291"
  },
  {
    "text": "I think it's easier to understand with an example. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=296"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let me demonstrate how you can replace ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=299"
  },
  {
    "text": "your UIButton with CLLocationButton. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=301"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this UIButton example, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=304"
  },
  {
    "text": "I will create a simple button that requests for location ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=306"
  },
  {
    "text": "by first requesting when-in-use authorization upon button tap. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=309"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll begin by instantiating a UIButton ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=314"
  },
  {
    "text": "and setting it's title to \"Current Location”. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=316"
  },
  {
    "text": "I wanna add a target-action that calls a function ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=319"
  },
  {
    "text": "and do the necessary action we want ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=322"
  },
  {
    "text": "every time a button is tapped. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=324"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this case, I wanna display all the parks nearby. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=326"
  },
  {
    "text": "So let's call this function \"showNearByParks”.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=330"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this showNearByParks function, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=335"
  },
  {
    "text": "I will use locationManager ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=337"
  },
  {
    "text": "to call requestWhenInUseAuthorization ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=339"
  },
  {
    "text": "and startUpdatingLocation. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=341"
  },
  {
    "text": "Within this function, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=344"
  },
  {
    "text": "I will also add additional logic ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=345"
  },
  {
    "text": "to render the map view accordingly. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=347"
  },
  {
    "text": "But, for simplicity, let's omit that. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=349"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's begin by replacing UIButton ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=352"
  },
  {
    "text": "by removing the first two lines ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=354"
  },
  {
    "text": "and replacing it with an instantiation ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=357"
  },
  {
    "text": "of CLLocationButton ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=359"
  },
  {
    "text": "and then setting the label to \".currentLocation”. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=360"
  },
  {
    "text": "Lastly, we can comment out the call ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=363"
  },
  {
    "text": "to requestWhenInUseAuthorization, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=366"
  },
  {
    "text": "and that's because the Location Button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=368"
  },
  {
    "text": "will grant a one-time authorization ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=370"
  },
  {
    "text": "on your behalf every time a button is successfully tapped.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=373"
  },
  {
    "text": "So if you have an existing UIButton, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=377"
  },
  {
    "text": "replacing it will be as simple as shown here. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=380"
  },
  {
    "text": "But we wanna make it even easier, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=383"
  },
  {
    "text": "so you can see an example of the Park Finder app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=385"
  },
  {
    "text": "attached to this talk.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=388"
  },
  {
    "text": "For those with SwiftUI apps, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=390"
  },
  {
    "text": "the Location Button is also in SwiftUI. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=391"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can use LocationButton as shown in the example here. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=394"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'd like to point out ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=397"
  },
  {
    "text": "that I am using SwiftUI's new \"symbolVariant\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=399"
  },
  {
    "text": "to set the arrow type, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=402"
  },
  {
    "text": "and \"tint\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=403"
  },
  {
    "text": "to set the background color of the button.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=404"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's go through some examples ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=409"
  },
  {
    "text": "on how you can customize Location Button. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=411"
  },
  {
    "text": "With our Location Button, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=413"
  },
  {
    "text": "you are able to customize the background color, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=415"
  },
  {
    "text": "the text and glyph color, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=417"
  },
  {
    "text": "the rounded corners, and so forth. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=418"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here are just some example styles ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=421"
  },
  {
    "text": "that you can create with our button. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=423"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's go through step-by-step examples ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=425"
  },
  {
    "text": "of customizing Location Button. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=427"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's start with our default button. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=429"
  },
  {
    "text": "The default look has \"Current Location\" title ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=431"
  },
  {
    "text": "in white ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=433"
  },
  {
    "text": "and a systemBlue background color, as shown here.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=434"
  },
  {
    "text": "We can set the button icon to arrowFilled.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=439"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, we can change the foreground color of the icon ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=443"
  },
  {
    "text": "by setting tintColor from white to black... ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=446"
  },
  {
    "text": "and then setting the backgroundColor to white. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=450"
  },
  {
    "text": "And lastly, I can set the corner radius ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=454"
  },
  {
    "text": "to have rounded corners by setting it to 25.0.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=456"
  },
  {
    "text": "And depending on how you set the constraints ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=461"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the sizing for the button, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=463"
  },
  {
    "text": "if the button's width is equal to the height, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=465"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can create a perfect circle ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=468"
  },
  {
    "text": "when the corner radius is half of the width. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=469"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, we turned our default location button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=473"
  },
  {
    "text": "into a white circular button with just simple adjustments. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=475"
  },
  {
    "text": "We've just gone through some stylistic changes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=479"
  },
  {
    "text": "that you can add to Location Button. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=481"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can customize the button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=483"
  },
  {
    "text": "to create the perfect look that fits your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=485"
  },
  {
    "text": "However, with great power comes great responsibility. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=488"
  },
  {
    "text": "When customizing your Location Button, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=491"
  },
  {
    "text": "there are some restrictions that you might encounter ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=493"
  },
  {
    "text": "to ensure that your Location Button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=496"
  },
  {
    "text": "is clear and visible. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=498"
  },
  {
    "text": "I wanna talk about some examples ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=500"
  },
  {
    "text": "that you can expect ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=502"
  },
  {
    "text": "if your button does not seem to be drawn correctly ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=504"
  },
  {
    "text": "or receive any location. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=507"
  },
  {
    "text": "If that's the case, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=509"
  },
  {
    "text": "while your target-action will be called, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=510"
  },
  {
    "text": "you won't get authorization.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=512"
  },
  {
    "text": "But don't worry. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=515"
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll give plenty of feedback with log messages ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=516"
  },
  {
    "text": "to help you figure out ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=518"
  },
  {
    "text": "what restrictions you're encountering. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=520"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=522"
  },
  {
    "text": "these are just different log messages ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=523"
  },
  {
    "text": "that refer to the insufficiency of the button sizing, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=525"
  },
  {
    "text": "alpha value, and color contrast ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=528"
  },
  {
    "text": "between tintColor and backgroundColor. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=530"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now let's go through some examples ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=533"
  },
  {
    "text": "of what feedback you can expect ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=535"
  },
  {
    "text": "if you're using Interface Builder in Xcode. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=536"
  },
  {
    "text": "Continuing with the button I have created earlier, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=539"
  },
  {
    "text": "if I was to change the existing button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=542"
  },
  {
    "text": "to have a white tintColor, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=544"
  },
  {
    "text": "people will not be able to see this ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=546"
  },
  {
    "text": "because the button's background color is already white. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=548"
  },
  {
    "text": "So if you do this, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=551"
  },
  {
    "text": "you will see this issue shown in the navigation pane ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=552"
  },
  {
    "text": "under the Issue tab in Xcode. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=555"
  },
  {
    "text": "Instead, let's revert our original button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=557"
  },
  {
    "text": "and try to change the opacity, or alpha, of this button. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=560"
  },
  {
    "text": "Maybe you can see this, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=564"
  },
  {
    "text": "but to others, it's a little too transparent, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=565"
  },
  {
    "text": "and so it fails our accessibility guidelines. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=568"
  },
  {
    "text": "A similar issue statement is produced in Xcode, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=571"
  },
  {
    "text": "recommending you to increase the alpha value. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=574"
  },
  {
    "text": "Another issue you might encounter ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=577"
  },
  {
    "text": "is insufficient button sizing. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=579"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is when the content of the button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=582"
  },
  {
    "text": "is too small or too large for the button size. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=584"
  },
  {
    "text": "Depending on the user's localization setting, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=588"
  },
  {
    "text": "the button's text length can change. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=591"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now let's increase the text size by changing the language.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=594"
  },
  {
    "text": "Depending on whether your implementation ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=601"
  },
  {
    "text": "is Auto-layout friendly, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=603"
  },
  {
    "text": "if we change the language, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=605"
  },
  {
    "text": "the size of the text could outgrow the button. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=606"
  },
  {
    "text": "Notice that the text does not fit the button in German. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=609"
  },
  {
    "text": "If this happens, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=612"
  },
  {
    "text": "look at the log messages for feedback. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=614"
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't forget to test your Location Button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=616"
  },
  {
    "text": "with really small or really large text sizes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=619"
  },
  {
    "text": "as well as testing it in different languages ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=622"
  },
  {
    "text": "to ensure that your button is working in all cases. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=624"
  },
  {
    "text": "So, when customizing your button, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=628"
  },
  {
    "text": "remember that it's imperative that it's clear and visible. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=630"
  },
  {
    "text": "If your button does not seem to be drawn correctly ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=634"
  },
  {
    "text": "or receive location, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=637"
  },
  {
    "text": "it could be that it's no longer legible. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=638"
  },
  {
    "text": "If that's the case, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=641"
  },
  {
    "text": "we provide log messages for guidance ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=642"
  },
  {
    "text": "to help you determine what could be wrong.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=644"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now that you know how to implement Location Button, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=648"
  },
  {
    "text": "you might wonder how it will affect ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=650"
  },
  {
    "text": "your existing authorization status. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=652"
  },
  {
    "text": "As I mentioned before, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=655"
  },
  {
    "text": "Location Button is essentially giving you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=657"
  },
  {
    "text": "Allow-Once authorization. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=659"
  },
  {
    "text": "If your app does not have any authorization status ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=661"
  },
  {
    "text": "of any kind, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=664"
  },
  {
    "text": "it will have \"NotDetermined\" authorization ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=665"
  },
  {
    "text": "with \"When I Share\" selected in Privacy Settings.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=668"
  },
  {
    "text": "If this is your app's current state, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=672"
  },
  {
    "text": "then the very first time ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=674"
  },
  {
    "text": "each user presses a Location Button, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=676"
  },
  {
    "text": "this prompt will ask them to confirm that they're on board. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=679"
  },
  {
    "text": "However, if your app is already authorized for location, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=682"
  },
  {
    "text": "such as \"While Using the App\" state, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=685"
  },
  {
    "text": "then using Location Button will not change ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=688"
  },
  {
    "text": "your existing state ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=691"
  },
  {
    "text": "and will behave like any other UIButton. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=692"
  },
  {
    "text": "Where it works, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=694"
  },
  {
    "text": "Location Button can feel magical and also reassuring, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=696"
  },
  {
    "text": "because you're letting people decide ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=699"
  },
  {
    "text": "when and whether their location will be used each time. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=701"
  },
  {
    "text": "Since Location Button is much more comfortable, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=704"
  },
  {
    "text": "we think people will be more likely to give your app location ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=707"
  },
  {
    "text": "via Location Button than they were previously. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=711"
  },
  {
    "text": "So we wanna give users and your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=714"
  },
  {
    "text": "another chance to get off on the right foot.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=717"
  },
  {
    "text": "If someone, who has chosen \"Don't Allow\" authorization ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=720"
  },
  {
    "text": "on your app in the past ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=723"
  },
  {
    "text": "taps our new Location Button, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=724"
  },
  {
    "text": "they will see this button introduction prompt ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=727"
  },
  {
    "text": "and have the opportunity ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=729"
  },
  {
    "text": "to move your app back to NotDetermined ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=731"
  },
  {
    "text": "and use Location Button going on forward. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=733"
  },
  {
    "text": "So in this session, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=735"
  },
  {
    "text": "I talked about bringing more dynamic abilities ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=737"
  },
  {
    "text": "to your watchOS apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=740"
  },
  {
    "text": "with Region-based user notifications. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=741"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you're interested in learning more, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=744"
  },
  {
    "text": "don't forget to view the resources with the session. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=745"
  },
  {
    "text": "We've also covered some cool new features ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=748"
  },
  {
    "text": "that can change the game of how you can ask for location.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=750"
  },
  {
    "text": "Giving people more control over their data privacy ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=754"
  },
  {
    "text": "is important to Apple. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=757"
  },
  {
    "text": "People are increasingly more aware ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=759"
  },
  {
    "text": "of how their data is being shared. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=761"
  },
  {
    "text": "When designing your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=763"
  },
  {
    "text": "to provide the most amazing user experience, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=765"
  },
  {
    "text": "but also build trust with your customers, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=767"
  },
  {
    "text": "you might want to ask yourself: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=770"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Does my app require traditional authorization, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=772"
  },
  {
    "text": "or would a one-time location authorization ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=776"
  },
  {
    "text": "with Location Button be more suitable?\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=778"
  },
  {
    "text": "And the answer, in some cases, might be that once is enough. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=782"
  },
  {
    "text": "With Location Button, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=787"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can gain trust with people ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=788"
  },
  {
    "text": "by giving more control ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=790"
  },
  {
    "text": "about when they want to share their location. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=791"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=794"
  },
  {
    "text": "[music]",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10102/?time=795"
  }
